Title: Damascena
Writer: Maria Laleva, Hristian Nochev, Alexander Smolyanov, Stoyan Stoyanov
Actors: Veselin Plachkov, Dimitar Banenkin, Neda Spasova, Simona Halacheva
Plot: The story follows a young boy's life which started in the Rose Valley. Nowadays - a grown up man, struggling to make his dream come true.
